==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Laputan
<hw>La*pu"tan</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
Laputa, an imaginary flying island described in <xex>Gulliver's
Travels</xex> as the home of chimerical philosophers.</def>
<specif>Hence,</specif> <def>fanciful; preposterous; absurd in science
or philosophy.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Laputan</xex> ideas.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>G.
Eliot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lap-welded</ent>⟦br⟧
